
---

## Additional Step: Update Bot Logger to Store Logs in MongoDB

In your bot's `utils/logger.py`, add this line inside `log_to_mod_channel` after sending to Discord:

```python
await db.database.mod_logs.insert_one({
    "guild_id": guild.id,
    "action": action,
    "moderator_id": moderator.id,
    "target_id": target.id if target else None,
    "reason": details,
    "timestamp": datetime.utcnow()
})
